🚀 **Excited to share my latest AI project!**

Over the past few days, I've been working on an **AI-powered Flight Intelligence Platform**—an application designed to help travelers make smarter booking decisions instead of simply tracking flight prices.

Most flight search platforms notify users when prices change. I wanted to go a step further by exploring how AI can transform the entire flight booking experience.

Some of the features I've been building include:

✈️ Real-time flight price tracking
📈 Historical fare trends (daily, monthly, and yearly)
🤖 AI-powered price predictions and buy-or-wait recommendations
💰 Intelligent deal scoring and savings insights
📅 Fare calendar to identify the cheapest travel dates
🛫 Flexible date and nearby airport recommendations
🔔 Instant notifications for significant price changes
📊 Interactive dashboards for smarter travel decisions

This project has been a great opportunity to combine **Business Analysis, Data Analytics, AI, and modern application development** into one practical solution.

One of the biggest lessons I've learned is that AI isn't just about automation—it's about helping people make better, data-driven decisions.

